## Session start prompt
```
Read CLAUDE.md, LOOP.md, PROGRESS.md. Pick up the next item in PROGRESS.md.
1. CONTEXT: delegate any non-trivial investigation to the `explorer` subagent;
   work from its digest, don't read the whole tree yourself.
2. PLAN: propose a plan, then send it to the `plan-critic` subagent. Apply its
   PROCEED-WITH-CHANGES items; if it says RECONSIDER, revise before coding.
   (Autonomous mode: act on the critic instead of waiting for a human.)
3. IMPLEMENT: make the change, then have the `verifier` subagent run [check].
4. REVIEW: send the diff to the `reviewer` subagent. Fix every correctness issue
   it returns; loop 3–4 until verifier PASS and reviewer says LGTM.
5. Update PROGRESS.md and run the learning pass. Print ALL ITEMS COMPLETE only
   when every item is done and the check passes.
```

